projectGridLines.title: Infra Automation
projectGridLines.description:
Description: Predictive Maintenance-In infrastructure development, AI-driven predictive maintenance is

crucial. It helps detect potential equipment failures before they occur, reducing downtime and improving

efficiency

Skill sets: Java AWS Full Stack with ReactJS

Traits expectation: Coding Skills, Excellent Communication and Client Interaction

Expected learning: JavaReactJS

Specific courses required for project execution: ReactJS

projectGridLines.title: OEM-Based Solutions
projectGridLines.description:
Description: These projects involve collaborating with external clients who require original equipment

manufacturing (OEM) solutions. Focus on Product Design - Creating intelligent, connected devices tailored

to client specifications, Prototyping and Testing-Iteratively developing and validating prototypes, Supply

Chain Integration-Ensuring seamless production and distribution and Quality Assurance - Rigorous testing

to meet industry standards

Skill sets: Embedded System Hardware design and development along with Java

Traits expectation: Design

Expected learning: Embedded System

Specific courses required for project execution: Embedded Systemand Java
